# Workspace (`/home/ken/ws`)

Multi-repo workspace for Ken Seehart (ken@agi.green). Cursor root is `/home/ken/ws`.

## Before coding

1. Read **`/home/ken/ws/AGENTS.md`** for the project map
2. Read the target project's **`AGENTS.md`**
3. For shared UI/MCP/templates, read **`/home/ken/ws/shared/AGENTS.md`**

## Shared layer

**`/home/ken/ws/shared`** holds cross-project assets:

- `web/chat/` — Claude-style chat widget (zero build)
- `templates/` — AGENTS.md and rule starters
- `mcp/starter_server.py` — FastMCP boilerplate
- `mcp/github/` — shared GitHub MCP (issues, PRs, repos)

Do not add RabbitMQ, Vue, or Docker requirements for new web work.

## MCP

Local servers: `/home/ken/ws/.cursor/mcp.json`. Remote (Claude mobile): OAuth HTTP on my.hosting.com — pattern in `tesla/`.

## Python / CLI

Shared uv env: **`~/.local/share/uv/global`** + command wrappers in **`~/.local/bin`**. Run **`global_setup`** after clone or when adding a project, then **`init_workspace --force`** for Cursor rules and root AGENTS.md symlinks. **`daime`** keeps its own `.venv` (GPU). See **`cli-commands`** rule and **`/home/ken/ws/AGENTS.md`**.

Global tools from `/home/ken/ws/util`: `whip`, `mkdo`, `mkpy`, `global_setup`.

## Anti-patterns

- WIX / heavy CMS for personal sites
- Rebuilding agi.green's full stack for simple chat UIs
- Monorepo merging unrelated projects
- Leaving `*:Zone.Identifier` files (Windows download markers in WSL) — delete on sight
